MID: bc3b1411634c493dbc771ae4c8bc3b14
UID: SDOC-LLR-192
STATUS: Active
TITLE: Markdown files discovery
STATEMENT: >>>
StrictDoc shall discover Markdown files ``*.md`` and ``*.markdown`` using the same mechanism as used for SDoc files.
<<<
